                    "statement-id": "cm-6_smt.b",
                    "uuid": "8df5b586-c7af-428d-b200-805151814ff4",
                    "description": "OpenShift as part of this information system supports {{ insert: param, cm-6_prm_1 }}. OpenShift is configured to properly enforced logical quotas to prevent full use of OpenShift host volumes on the underlying Kubernetes' nodes in the cluster by use of soft eviction settings."
